text:
Comedian Goes Viral After Sharing Nude Photo With Son 1 hour ago share 
A comedian by the name of Jess posted what she believed to be an amazing photo of her with her lil man on Instagram. This photo did not sit well with some and goes of course gone viral with the mom being dragged. 
While some say it's inappropriate, some find it perfectly OK for her to pose nude with her son. 
What do you think? A post shared by ✨Princess Of Comedy ✨ (@jesshilarious_official) on Feb 23, 2017 at 3:34pm PST Contact
